<h5 class="au-display-md">
  <b class="sapphire">Licenses</b>
</h5>
<p>
  Add the name of a license that will be of relevance to a buyer.
</p>
<p>
  {{seller-form/multi-text
    field=(mut form.licenses)
    signal=form.signal
    theme="sapphire"
    thin=true
  }}
</p>
<p>
  Provide supporting documents for the above licenses.
</p>
<p>
  {{dds/file-upload
    name="license_document"
    field=(mut form.license_document_ids)
    fileService=fileService
    signal=form.signal
    multiple=true
    theme="sapphire"
    thin=true
  }}
</p>
<hr class="super-light">
<h5 class="au-display-md">
  <b class="sapphire">Accreditations</b>
</h5>
<p>
  Add the name of an accrediting authority and an accreditation, that will be of value to a buyer. Membership of government schemes and panels are not considered accreditations. 
</p>
<p>
  {{seller-form/multi-text
    field=(mut form.accreditations)
    signal=form.signal
    theme="sapphire"
    thin=true
  }}
</p>
<p>
  Provide supporting documents for the above accreditations.
</p>
<p>
  {{dds/file-upload
    name="accreditation_document"
    field=(mut form.accreditation_document_ids)
    fileService=fileService
    signal=form.signal
    multiple=true
    theme="sapphire"
    thin=true
  }}
</p>
<hr class="super-light">
<h5 class="au-display-md">
  <b class="sapphire">Industry engagements</b>
</h5>
<p>
  Are you involved in any industry boards, committees or groups? 
</p>
<p>
  {{seller-form/multi-text
    field=(mut form.engagements)
    signal=form.signal
    theme="sapphire"
    thin=true
  }}
</p>
<hr class="super-light">
<h5 class="au-display-md">
  <b class="sapphire">Awards</b>
</h5>
<p>
  Add the name of an award and sponsor that will be of relevance to a buyer. 
</p>
<p>
  {{seller-form/multi-text
    field=(mut form.awards)
    signal=form.signal
    theme="sapphire"
    thin=true
  }}
</p>
